{"tid":2315263,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不予家奴！120萬劑支那製疫苗送交印尼政府準備大規模接種","createTime":"2020-12-07T05:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T05:53:00.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3944bb059a1de7549bd14be52fff17fa8f1929d8","tid":2315263,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:45:08.000Z","msg":"印尼總統佐科威（Joko Widodo）表示，該國今天收到<br />\n來自中國的首批2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19）疫苗，政府正為大規模疫苗接種計畫進行<br />\n準備。<br />\n <br />\n路透社報導，佐科威在線上簡報時指出，印尼已收到來自北京科興生物製品公司（Sinovac<br />\n Biotech）的120萬劑疫苗，政府打算明年1月初再接收來自該公司的另外180萬劑疫苗。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202012070003.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202012070003.aspx&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=fadb1855\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202012070003.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"5ef61dd207d0f8dc92530906173c1001d984ce41","tid":2315263,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:48:21.000Z","msg":"賤過印印<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1aefab9b3ee470a0f9245eaaa0d40b48784412","tid":2315263,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ef61dd207d0f8dc92530906173c1001d984ce41","tid":2315263,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:48:21.000Z","msg":"賤過印印<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:50:05.000Z","msg":"錯，佢係唔忍心用中國人黎做實驗，好佛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c88f77eda6c6379fe91dd5b2d41d6e37e72e9e","tid":2315263,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:53:00.000Z","msg":"呢隻多多真係共匪黎"}]}